    question: "Can dojo software track multiple martial arts?",
    answer: "Yes, quality dojo software supports multiple disciplines with separate rank tracks. A school teaching both Karate and Judo can maintain independent belt progressions, testing schedules, and curriculum requirements for each art while sharing student accounts and billing. You can configure different kyu/dan systems, belt colors, and testing criteria per discipline. Students training in multiple arts see all their progressions in one unified profile.",
