    answer: "Dojo management software typically costs £50-200 per month depending on student count and features. Smaller dojos (under 100 students) often find suitable options at £50-80 monthly. Mid-size schools (100-250 students) pay £80-120. Larger schools with advanced features or multiple locations may pay £120-200. Per-student pricing models charge £1-3 per active student. MyDojo offers £79/month flat-rate for unlimited students.",
